Hey there!
We created a model with Axon to detect game pieces on the field.
We tested the model on the Axon framework and it had proved to be working.
We tried integrating the model with the PI following the instructions that were given in the Axon guide with the example Python program.
The model didn’t seem to work and detect the game pieces.
Any advice?
Thanks!
